Buying a Christmas present for a tech fan is surprisingly simple. Firstly, ask them what they want. Request that they provide you with a detailed description, a picture of the product, and a link to where you can buy it online. Then you buy them the item. It’s truly that simple. If you really need to choose the gift yourself, make sure you know which platform the person games on – PC, PlayStation 4, or Xbox One – and what other hardware they already own. Alternatively, find out what other tech products would interest them – such as a Raspberry Pi computer. To help you make the best choice possible, we have listed a range of awesome PC gift options for this festive season. <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-311137" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Raspberry-Pi-4-Model-B-1.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Raspberry-Pi-4-Model-B-1.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Raspberry-Pi-4-Model-B-1-300x202.jpg 300w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Raspberry-Pi-4-Model-B-1-595x400.jpg 595w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-331840" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/gamdias-hermes-p1-640x430.png" alt="gamdias hermes p1" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/gamdias-hermes-p1-640x430.png 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/gamdias-hermes-p1-595x400.png 595w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/gamdias-hermes-p1-300x202.png 300w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/gamdias-hermes-p1-768x516.png 768w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/gamdias-hermes-p1.png 912w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, 